Class PartOfSpeechNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • PartOfSpeechNode
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    $Node, CCNode, CDNode, DTNode, EXNode, FWNode, INNode, integrateNode, JJNode, LSNode, MDNode, NNNode, PDTNode, POSNode, PRP$Node, PRPNode, RBNode, RPNode, SYMNode, TONode, transformNode, UHNode, VBNode, WDTNode, WP$Node, WPNode, WRBNode

    public class PartOfSpeechNode
extends java.lang.Object
    A high-level class for representing the hierarchy of POS tags. Both the names and the hierarchy is taken from the Penn TreeBank set of POS tags. Because the nodes are meant to represent a dependency parse, each has one governor and 0 or more dependents.
    Author:
    Max Lotstein
